Class Alloy

    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Alloy

    public class Alloy
extends SlimefunItem
    Represents an alloy, a SlimefunItem obtainable using the Smeltery.

    An alloy is generally made up of several minerals. As an example, a BRASS_INGOT is made up of COPPER_DUST, ZINC_DUST and COPPER_INGOT.

    Author:
    TheBusyBiscuit
